@(92-114=c24214.92) As for you, lie in sleep! May your palm tree, extending its fronds, spread joy like a fig tree (?). Place coals (?) beside @wSN{Urim}! Place charcoal beside @wSN{Unug}! Seize the enemy's mouth like ……! Bind his arms like reed bundles! Make the enemy cower before you, lest he rip open your back like a sack,
